  "title": "fix(configure): update lifecycle state",
  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThis fixes the lifecycle of `connectConfigure`.\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- `getConfiguration` returns a state computed with `SearchParameters`\r\n- `refine` relies on `mergeSearchParameters` directly instead of passing a virtual widget to `enhanceConfiguration`\r\n- `removeSearchParameters` was removed from the widget scope to not pollute it\r\n- `connectConfigure` tests now also check that search parameters are resolved correctly (e.g. with facets as an array)",
